title: Midterm Cram: Florida & Beyond (ft. Ali Vitali)
description:
For the final edition of Midterm Cram, recorded on Friday, November 9, Sal Gentile and Henry Melcher talk to Ali Vitali of NBC News about the recount situation in Florida as well as what to expect from the new makeup of Congress.

Ali's interview begins at 9:20.
